hen you feel lucky&quot; to get on the spot instrucetd by the map. NOTE: NO FORM OF LEVITATE WHILE BEING FLUXXED if you are not aggroed, look straight ahead from the zone direction. see that thing sticking up? that just goes above your eye level? levitate yourself, and go over to it. you are now safe, with a view of the rampart to the skele room.<br><br>okay, now take the person you intend on having charm the skel, and have him stand at zone NOT ON THE BRIDGE. if you have another chanter thats great. have them stand on the bridge with all stuns/meses loaded. (note: there is an 85% chance that that enchanter will DIE, bring a cleric)<br><br>Here it gets tricky. when all the mobs are clear from your path, float down to the rampart. target the thing using the trick i told you above (the one to see if skel is up) then approach the door. open the door and immobilize your target. the human skeleton will attack. run back to where you fluxxed on the rampart and float down to the bridge.<br>stay with your enc(rooting unessential mobs) if you have one, untill the human skeleton is down on the bridge. now, run back to the zone line. NOTHING SHOULD HAVE FOLLOWED YOU. there is a bug, where they get stuck on that little lantern. IF YOU ARE NOT FOLLOWED, DO NOT ZONE. IF YOU ARE FOLLOWED ROUND THE LANTERN AGAIN (and for god sakes, get a heal if possible)<br><br>if all goes well and there is a train of mobs stuck on the lantern, its time to get funky. have your charmer lead charm, and attempt to target the human skele. just do something to piss it off, will probally dislodge it from the lantern. (here you might want to ask someone who acutally pulled CoM to do it, or tell you how) then simply have the skel charmed, give it the bottle, and get outta there!<br><br>Enjoy!<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uialinudaetarien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ialinu DaeTarien